            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Personal Portraits</head>
                <origin>New York Tribune</origin>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <commentary>"The Charlestown correspondent of the New York Tribune gives the
                    subjoined sketches of the two prosecuting attorneys at the recent trials at that
                    place. The intelligent readers will of course make all due allowance for the
                    abolition proclivities of the writer."</commentary>
                <names/>
                <summary>Sketches of the prosecuting attorneys and judge in the John Brown Trial, as
                    written by a correspondent for the New York Tribune.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/ssnov59.html#11.29a</note>
            </div>
