                        <pf>Capt.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Cadets from VMI, the West Augusta Guard and Spring Hill Mountain Guard were
                    all ordered to Charlestown on Saturday, November 26 because of fears that the
                    Harper's Ferry prisoners might either escape or be rescued.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/ssnov59.html#11.29d</note>
            </div>
