                <head>Governor Wise Criticised by a Fellow Democrat</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Albany Argus criticized Gov. Wise for his handling of the Harper's
                    Ferry raiders, arguing that he helped make them heroes.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/ssnov59.html#11.29j</note>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
